Devumi is one of the many online marketplaces selling fake engagement (Twitter follows, YouTube views, SoundCloud plays, etc ...).
        The services are very cheap, for just a few dollars you can for example purchase thousands of instagram followers.
        People willing to boost their social media following are increasingly buying these types of services in an attempt to give
        credit to their social media account, and kickstart a cycle of growth.
